data.description: Welcome to your dream townhome! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem boasts a one-car garage and a private patio, perfect for enjoying outdoor relaxation. Step inside to discover the epitome of elegance with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances adorning the gourmet kitchen. The spacious living area features gleaming hardwood floors, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The sunroom features a built-in bar with beverage refrigerator. Upstairs, the luxurious primary suite awaits, complete with a pristine ensuite bathroom and two walk in closets. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for guests or family members. With modern amenities and stylish finishes throughout, this townhome offers the ultimate in comfort and convenience. Don't miss the chance to make this your new home sweet home—schedule your viewing today! America's Preferred Home Warranty is included with acceptable offer.
